snippet.title: Pixelcalypse (intro)
snippet.description:
Attention! The game help improve memory and reflexes!
Simple, but fascinating pixel art game for improving memory and reflexes for the whole family. Dodge enemies, avoid obstacles and complete missions. All missions are different from each other. You will have artifacts that will give you time and units or will take it.
